---
Title: Love's Maturity
Author: Hadewijch of Antwerp
Source:
  - Title: The Soul Is Here for It's Own Joy
    ISBN: 9780880014755
    Page: 119
---
In the beginnning Love satisfies us.
THen Love first poke to me of love --
How I laughed at her in return!
But then she made me like the hazel trees,
Which blossom early in the season of darkness,
And bear fruit slowly.
